high_descs: Go across the room to face the shelf cabinet on the left corner
Pick up the green sponge from the shelf
Turn around and go to the stove
Put the sponge in the pot on the rear left of the stove
Pick up the pot with the sponge in it
Take the pot to the table at the opposite side of the room
Place the pot on the table

turn around and walk forwards to the fridge on the right, then take a left and walk over to the stove on the left up ahead
place the sponge inside of the pot on the back left burner
pick the pot off of the stove with the sponge in it on the back left burner

high_descs: Go across the room to the wooden shelf in the left corner.
Pick up the green sponge on the left of the top shelf.
Turn around walk across the room, the make a left at the refrigerator and go to the stove across from you.
Place the sponge in the large pot on the back, left burner of the stove.
Pick up the large black pot with the sponge inside it, from the stove.
Turn to your right and go across the room, then turn right at the counter and go to the end of it, then make a left, go to the window, turn to your right and go to the table.
Place the pot with the sponge inside it on the back of the table, behind the two coffee cups.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot containing a sponge on the table.
